    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.18))
    v0 = v2
    v1 = (v0 * ((v2 + 0.38 + v1 + 0.43) - tmp))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v2 + 0.24) / (v0 + 0.35 / v1 + 0.34)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.33 + v2 + 0.89)) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.05) * (v0 + 0.36 * v1 + 0.59)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.82) * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.43) * 0.55))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.46 + v0 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
